cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.DB 

The paper discusses the propagation of individual interests along social networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of social networks (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper introduces the notion of "Semantic Multiplex", which is a concept that relates to the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.SI and cs.SOC, followed by cs.IR, cs.DL, and cs.DB.
